. 
<emphasis box="[591,691,1793,1818]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">minimus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Rozkosny" box="[698,1005,1793,1819]" pageId="22" pageNumber="30" refString="Rozkosny, R. &amp; Kovac, D. (1997) Ptecticus minimus, a new species of Sarginae from West Malaysia including the description of its larva and puparium (Diptera Stratiomyidae). The Raffles Bulletin of Zoology, 45 (1), 39 - 51." type="journal article" year="1997">
